@database LampClass
@index "Classes.guide/Main"

@Node Main "RxMUI - Lamp Class"


Lamp class    @{"Index" link "Classes.guide/Main"} @{"Super" link "AreaClass.guide/Main"}
@{u}                                                             @{uu}

  The Lamp class is used to create those cute little lamps.

  Lamp is a subclass of Lamp.mcc so you must have Lamp.mcc in
  MUI:Libs/MUI to use it. Lamp.mcc is copyright of Maik
  Schreiber.

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Attributes@{ub}

  @{fg shine}Color@{fg text}
  M ISGN G2N
  A number or one of:
     o Off
     o OK
     o Warning
     o Error
     o FatalError
     o Processing
     o LookingUp
     o Connecting
     o SendingData
     o ReceivingData
     o LoadingData
     o SavingData

  @{fg shine}Type@{fg text}
  S I
  One of:
     o Tiny
     o Small
     o Medium
     o Big
     o Huge

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Methods@{ub}

  None defined

@EndNode
